## ✅ ALWAYS DO
- Check existing files before creating new ones
- Tell me which files you will CREATE, MODIFY, and NOT TOUCH before starting
- Keep components small and focused (max ~100 lines)
- Add loading.tsx for routes with async data
- Use async/await — never .then().catch()

## ❌ NEVER DO
- Use "any" TypeScript type
- Use pages/ directory
- Use deprecated @supabase/auth-helpers
- Touch unrelated files
- Over-engineer simple features

## 📝 COMMIT FORMAT
feat: add new feature
fix: bug fix
chore: config/dependencies
refactor: restructure without behavior change
style: styling only

## 🔔 TASK COMPLETION
After completing ANY task, always end your final message with:
